kotak obatnya lupa dibawa.

474
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:18,230
Mengapa ceroboh sekali?

475
00:26:18,470 --> 00:26:19,950
Sudah begitu dewasa. Ini… ini… ini…

476
00:26:20,190 --> 00:26:21,040
Kalian…

477
00:26:23,190 --> 00:26:24,040
Ayu,

478
00:26:24,190 --> 00:26:25,560
