479
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,760
harus bagaimana?

480
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:28,400
Nenek Sun, jangan khawatir,

481
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,680
aku punya obat rebusan bunga coptis
dan huang bai.

482
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:33,920
Meminumnya bisa menawarkan racun kemalakian.

483
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:38,280
Hampir saja.

484
00:26:38,430 --> 00:26:39,400
Ini, ini, ini.

485
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:40,830
Terima kasih, ya.

486
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:53,680
Ayu,

487
00:26:54,310 --> 00:26:55,950
mohon maaf untuk masalah tadi,

488
00:26:56,190 --> 00:26:57,160
telah salah paham padamu.

489
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:59,230
Tidak apa-apa. Tidak apa-apa.

490
00:26:59,470 --> 00:27:00,920
Nona Ayu sungguh berlapang dada.

491
