makanya aku tahu perbedaannya.

505
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:43,560
(Qingqing,)

506
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:44,560
(saat aku merawat luka,)

507
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:46,040
