529
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:54,680
karena suka.

530
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:56,430
Ada apa denganmu?

531
00:28:57,430 --> 00:28:58,400
Tidak apa-apa, tidak apa-apa.

532
00:29:01,560 --> 00:29:02,950
