569
00:31:43,230 --> 00:31:44,880
Kakak Yuchi.

570
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,070
Mengapa masih belum memanggilku?

571
00:32:08,520 --> 00:32:10,040
Mungkinkah karena stoplesnya hilang?

